Aggro management is my first lesson given when hunting in a new groupo, or MA'ing a open raid.<br>
<br>
AM(agro manage) is <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">ENTIRLY</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> the groups'/ raid obligation. My blood boils when im criticised about my ability to control it, when the criticism comes from a knucklehead that doesnt understand this. Many caster types that maybe new, think Taunt is auot peel, and we all know it isnt.<br>
<br>
My current setup is Snowchipper -pri-  Frosty-off-<br>
